Expences Bundle
===============

Allows to control and visualise your daily expences

Installation
------------

# Add entry to deps file
    [WowoExpencesBundle]
        git=/home/wowo/localhost/WowoExpencesBundle/
        target=/bundles/Wowo/ExpencesBundle

# Update vendors
    ./bin/vendors update

# Update autoloader script (app/autoload.php)
    $loader->registerNamespaces(array(
        'Wowo'             => __DIR__.'/../vendor/bundles',
        // [...]
    ));

# Turn on bundle in Kernel (app/AppKernel.php)
    $bundles = array(
        new Wowo\ExpencesBundle\WowoExpencesBundle(),
        // [...]
    );

